# EmailJS Configuration
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com and create a service + email template.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.

REACT_APP_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
REACT_APP_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
REACT_APP_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here

# ── Email Template Variables ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your EmailJS template should use these variables:
#   {{to_name}}      — Authority name entered by the caregiver
#   {{to_email}}     — Authority email (used as the "To" address)
#   {{user_name}}    — Full name of the monitored user
#   {{device_id}}    — Smart Stick device ID
#   {{location}}     — GPS coordinates (e.g. "6.5244°N, 3.3792°E")
#   {{area}}         — User's registered home area
#   {{time}}         — Date and time of the alert
#   {{message}}      — Optional additional message from the caregiver
#   {{snapshot_url}} — URL of the camera snapshot (or "No image")
